    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892100/extras/df04db3b2b17ba23fc43348a45ae7d65.avif?t=1769074033\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的战斗充满狂暴的打击感。玩家可以使用赤手撕碎敌人、以利刃斩杀、重锤碾压，并施展血腥终结技，消灭敌军。面对成群的敌人，玩家必须以灵活多变的方式杀出重围，体验前所未有的战斗快感。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892100/extras/c1fdea3001693913e1618220aa98d975.poster.avif?t=1769074033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892100/extras/c1fdea3001693913e1618220aa98d975.webm?t=1769074033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892100/extras/c1fdea3001693913e1618220aa98d975.mp4?t=1769074033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892100/extras/565b6c23078782fc69b95803e0deb916.avif?t=1769074033\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一名忍狐，莱昂拥有掌控“气”的超凡力量。游戏中的气贯穿于万物之中，赋予角色强大的技能和招式。玩家将学习并掌握多样化的忍狐技能，善加利用这些力量来战胜敌人，控制战局。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892100/extras/ae277810bac51ef085ca1d70bf566d96.poster.avif?t=1769074033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892100/extras/ae277810bac51ef085ca1d70bf566d96.webm?t=1769074033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892100/extras/ae277810bac51ef085ca1d70bf566d96.mp4?t=1769074033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892100/extras/40bf3812c8bd7786020e83bf897b35ae.avif?t=1769074033\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《修罗的杀阵》深受日本文化和神话启发，玩家将在游戏中遇见各种传说中的生物，选择与它们结盟或将其撕裂。这款游戏不仅展现了独特的日式美学，也提供了一场充满挑战和神秘的冒险之旅。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892100/extras/7b7e4e3ebaed1c379cce3b0ce7e78175.poster.avif?t=1769074033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892100/extras/7b7e4e3ebaed1c379cce3b0ce7e78175.webm?t=1769074033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892100/extras/7b7e4e3ebaed1c379cce3b0ce7e78175.mp4?t=1769074033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
